(1) To compile this project, run `make`

(2) This project has the following dependencies:
boost
utf8cpp
llvm
header file alloca.h (optional: see (3))

(3) This project has the following build options:
BUCKET_NO_ALLOCA          Set this flag if you are experiencing stack overflows
                          or your system does not provide the function alloca().
BUCKET_DEBUG              Compiles bucket in debug mode.
NDEBUG                    Compiles bucket in production mode.
BUCKET_HIGHLIGHTING_OFF   Turns off ANSI colors in error messages.

(4) This project has the following system/compiler requirements:
UNIX
c++17 compliant compiler (gcc or clang recommended)

(5) This code is highly experimental so don't expect it to build easily.
